sequenceDiagram
    participant App as 应用/pgx
    participant Exec as Executor
    participant BM as Buffer Manager
    participant SB as shared_buffers
    participant OS as OS Page Cache
    participant Disk as 文件/存储
    participant WAL as WAL

    App->>Exec: UPDATE ... WHERE id = $1
    Exec->>BM: ReadBuffer(BufferTag)
    BM->>SB: 查找目标 block
    alt shared buffer hit
        SB-->>BM: 已驻留 page，增加 pin
    else shared buffer miss
        BM->>OS: 发起文件 read
        alt OS cache hit
            OS-->>BM: 内存拷贝返回
        else OS cache miss
            OS->>Disk: 物理读取
            Disk-->>OS: block
            OS-->>BM: block
        end
    end
    BM-->>Exec: pinned buffer + content lock
    Exec->>Exec: 生成新 tuple version，判断 HOT
    Exec->>WAL: 生成 heap/索引相关 WAL record
    Exec->>SB: 修改 page，标记 dirty
    Exec->>BM: 释放 content lock 与 pin
    App->>WAL: COMMIT 需要满足相应 WAL 持久化策略
    Note over SB,Disk: heap dirty page 可稍后由 backend/background writer/checkpointer 写回
